task.summary: Creation of domain model classes and service interfaces for the "myphotos-model" module. Creating a dump of the "myphotos" database

Domain models and data storage models were created, and also, validation rules for entity components were established, which was achieved with using the Java Persistence and Bean Validation API from the JavaEE7-API library.

Used CDI annotations, created producers and added beans to the CDI container. Application properties have been configured. The application constants class and the enum ImageCategory class have been created.
EJB Service implementations PhotoServiceBean, ProfileServiceBean AccessTokenServiceBean
Home and Profile page handlers with mock data
JPA impl mocks, entity listeners and JPA xml config files
Additional components for test data generation
